phrases: Not a bad time, considering the weather.
Thought we were going to die out there.
No one ever said winter training would be this tough.
Damn it, I cannot feel my legs.
I wish they would let us inside already.
I bet they are busy putting together a huge feast for us!
She was sticking with Daz since he was not doing so well.
Maybe they are with the last squad?
The last squad, led by Thomas, just arrived.
You do not think... they got lost?
They do not stand a chance if they are stuck in this blizzard.
I am going back out to try and find them!
We will send a rescue team first thing in the morning.
It will be too late by then!
We will not make any more victims!
Daz already has one foot in the grave.
It is his own fault for doing this training to boost his score
without knowing how much his body can take.
He is just not cut out to be a soldier.
If you keep crawling to the foot of the mountain at this rate,
he will probably be a goner by then, and we would be lucky not to be.
Which means there is only two outcomes.
Leave Daz here and save ourselves, or all three of us die.
That your prediction is entirely wrong.
I will be able to reach our base at the foot of the mountain... with Daz.
You can go ahead of us and get back safe.
There is no trouble in it for you.
We will make it back for sure.
Why have not you asked me to help at all?
You have resigned yourself to death already.
You are hoping to die here, are not you?
I thought you were a good girl.
You have got to at least make it look like you are trying to save his life.
If you want people to remember you as a
hero who died trying to save someone,
do not drag him down with you.
That is what a bad girl would do.
The mistress' daughter who had people after your life.
So it was you after all.
It is something I happened to overhear.
At a church in the interior,
back when I snuck around borrowing things to stay alive.
What a sob story it was.
An illegitimate child cannot succeed a powerful noble.
So they just wanted to kill her, to end all the fuss once and for all.
But they would look aside if she changed her name and lived a humble life.
In the end, I heard the girl was forced to join the Cadet Corps.
I do not plan to either.
If that is the case... why?
You and me... have similar backgrounds?
That is the reason you became a soldier?
You have got to be kidding me.
You and I cannot even compare.
We both got a second chance at life.
But I am not the one who took on a fake name.
If I abandon my name and reject who I am, they win.
I am going to keep the name I have and make the best of my life.
That is the one and only way I can get my revenge.
So how do you explain yourself?
Are you going to commit suicide
and make everyone who ruined your life happy?
Why is your desire to kill aimed at yourself?
If you are so eager, use that passion to change your own fate!
There is no way the three of us can make it out of here alive.
I can see the base straight down from here.
We drop Daz off this cliff.
and hopefully someone down there finds him.
Sure, it might be a long shot, but...
he will be an icicle long before you drag him down.
But he will die for sure if he falls!
I will do it myself, so get moving already!
It is better if you guys do not come along.
Like our instructor said, you will only end up becoming more victims.
I am going so that does not happen.
I am not leaving Christa and the others.
What do you think you are doing?
You are going to need a lot more gear than that.
If you go by yourselves, you will be in the same pickle as Christa.
In a search, the more eyes, the better.
To be honest, we could use you.
I think we will be fine.
What was that sound just now?
I told Reiner and the others I would wait since you would come along eventually.
What a stupid thing I have done...
But you did not have any rope.
Even if you did, it is too high.
How did you get Daz down from there?
I think I can trust you.
When I reveal my secret to everyone, promise me.
Take back your old name and live.
That it would have been better if I was never born at all.
I was hated by the world just for existing.
To give countless people joy, I gave up my life.
But from that time, there was a wish I held in my heart.
If someday, I was given a second chance at life...

Do you think she is known about it?

But Ymir is like... she is aware of being a Titan all along.

Not in a place like this!
Do not pretend like you are good, you idiot!
You want to go out in a blaze of glory?
It is too late for you to try and get into heaven!

The rest of us will attack where the Titans are gathering!
